{
  "stem": "13469.7",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because I wanted to be an engineer, they thought the Midlands and Birmingham was the right place for me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the Jewish Refugees Committee arranged for me to come to Birmingham.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there I met a lady who was called Ruth [INAUDIBLE] at the time, later Ruth [INAUDIBLE], and she was a fantastic lady in the refugee movement, really, who really looked after me ever so well.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Unfortunately, she's passed away now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But she set me up in a hostel in Handsworth in Birmingham, where there were other refugees.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was run by a lady, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Miller.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "These were all people who came just before the war, really-- Mrs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Miller from Vienna and several of the boys who came there before the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And during the day, this Ruth [INAUDIBLE] arranged for me to get an apprenticeship at BSA Tools, a five-year engineering apprenticeship.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I went there for five years every day on my bike.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And in the evenings, I studied, first of all for university entrance for my matriculation, as they called it in those days.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the biggest problem I had with the matriculation-- I knew all the math and the science and all that sort of thing which you want to know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The biggest problem was the English, because I couldn't really speak English sufficiently well enough to write the answers and, and all that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had to do a lot to of catching up on the English.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I got my matriculation, and then there was an intermediate examination for bachelor of science.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was different from what it is now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And eventually, I embarked on an external London University degree course.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think they have those sort of things nowadays.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's open university now.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
